steps.html_instructions: Head southwest on Obala Lazareta toward Ul. Svetog Nikole
Obala kneza Domagoja turns slightly right and becomes Poljana kneza Trpimira
Ul. kralja Zvonimira turns slightly right and becomes Pojišanska ul.
Poljička cesta turns left and becomes Ul. Zbora narodne garde

Merge onto Most Smokovik/Ul. Zbora narodne garde
Continue to follow Ul. Zbora narodne garde
At the roundabout, take the 1st exit onto D1

At the roundabout, take the 3rd exit onto the A1 ramp to Zagreb/Rijeka/Dubrovnik/Šestanovac
Partial toll road

Keep left at the fork, follow signs for Zagreb/Šibenik/E65/A1 and merge onto A1/E65/E71
Partial toll road

Take exit 18-Zadar II toward Sukošan/Zadar Centar/Zračna luka Zemunik
Toll road
Take the D8 exit toward Sukošan/Bibinje/Zadar Centar/Luka Zadar
Keep right at the fork, follow signs for Zadar Centar and merge onto Jadranska Magistrala/D8
Turn left onto Ul. Braće Miroslava i Janka Perice
Head south on Ul. Josipa Jurja Strossmayera toward Ul. Stjepana Radića
Continue onto Ul. Braće Miroslava i Janka Perice
At the roundabout, take the 2nd exit

Continue onto D424 (signs for Zagreb/Split/Zračna luka/Repülőtér)
Partial toll road

Take the exit onto A1/E65/E71 toward Split/Šibenik
Partial toll road

Turn right
Destination will be on the left

Keep right at the fork, follow signs for Zagreb/Zadar/E65/A1 and merge onto A1/E65/E71
Continue to follow A1/E71
Partial toll road

Keep left at the fork to continue on E65/E71
Toll road

Keep left, follow signs for Zagreb
Toll road

Continue onto Jadranska avenija
Partial toll road
